Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.94,0:02:12.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}神山高中古籍研究社全員四人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.94,0:02:15.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}為什麼我們現在隨著定點巴士起伏呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.11,0:02:19.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}當然是跟這趟車的目的地有關係
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.49,0:02:21.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}作為終點的財前村
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.08,0:02:23.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}因登山和溫泉而出名
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.95,0:02:26.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我們此行目的不是登山而是為了去溫泉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.87,0:02:31.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}在暑假裡好好休息才是遵循我信條的行為 但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.83,0:02:35.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}叔叔那件事真是萬分感謝您 折木同學
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.71,0:02:38.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}難得放暑假 大家一起去泡溫泉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.51,0:02:41.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}一起去吧 溫泉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.26,0:02:41.34,shisseki,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(582,412)\fad(500,0)}想和大家一起去
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.26,0:02:41.34,shisseki,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(714,248)\fad(500,0)}想去
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.26,0:02:41.34,shisseki,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(774,450)\fad(500,0)}想去
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.26,0:02:41.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}唔咕
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.39,0:02:43.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}好…吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.22,0:02:47.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}迎接的人應該很快就來了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.98,0:02:50.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}呀 景色真棒
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.65,0:02:52.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那個 折木同學
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.52,0:02:53.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.77,0:02:54.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}暈了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.32,0:02:58.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}這點事就叫死叫活的 真不愧為奉太郎啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.44,0:03:00.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}才坐了一個半小時而已喔
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.32,0:03:01.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}真不像話
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.70,0:03:02.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}話說回來 摩耶花
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.70,0:03:03.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}還真給你找到住處了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.12,0:03:05.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}經營民宿旅館的親戚
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.12,0:03:10.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}現在正在改建不能開門迎客 所以可以免費借給我們用
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.25,0:03:14.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}折木同學 到了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.30,0:03:18.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}呀 到了 到了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.92,0:03:21.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}折木 不快點就把你扔下咯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.88,0:03:23.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}終於到了 我們的旅館
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.72,0:03:28.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}歡迎光臨青山荘
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.68,0:03:31.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}這邊是姐姐善名梨繪
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.64,0:03:33.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}這邊是妹妹善名嘉代
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.36,0:03:35.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}你們好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.36,0:03:37.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}上小學六年級和小學四年級了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.03,0:03:38.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}又長高…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.74,0:03:39.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\an8}嘿呀
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.49,0:03:42.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}房間在二樓的最裡面
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.74,0:03:47.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}哇 奉太郎 快過來 快過來
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.87,0:03:52.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}這個房間風景著實不錯啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.79,0:03:55.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}偶爾這樣也不壞
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.63,0:03:57.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}嘛 如果要奢侈點說
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.25,0:03:59.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}一個人來才算是能細細品味
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.38,0:04:03.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}奉太郎會單人旅行？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.68,0:04:04.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}哈 真會開玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.30,0:04:08.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}正是因為千反田策劃 摩耶花走了後門
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.77,0:04:11.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我們才能在這裡 這點請您勿忘
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.02,0:04:14.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}吃午飯了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.02,0:04:16.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}該吃飯了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.40,0:04:17.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}這樣說了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.77,0:04:18.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.91,0:04:24.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}起司嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.12,0:04:29.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}燉肉 奶汁烤起司 起司火鍋
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.54,0:04:31.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}涼拌的？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.04,0:04:32.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}一 二
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.12,0:04:34.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我開動了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.17,0:04:36.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}接下來還有甜點喔
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.88,0:04:38.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}起司蛋糕嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.96,0:04:40.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}你怎麼知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.25,0:04:41.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}聞到味道了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.42,0:04:42.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}好厲害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.92,0:04:44.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}厲害嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.09,0:04:45.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}跟摩耶花姐姐說的一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.43,0:04:47.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}你到底說了些什麼 伊原
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.89,0:04:49.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}明天大家一起去放煙火吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.93,0:04:50.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.72,0:04:52.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}是吧 昨天爸爸…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.52,0:04:55.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}你在幹些什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.73,0:04:56.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}姐姐 對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.15,0:04:57.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}拿去
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.56,0:04:59.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.65,0:05:00.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}沒燙著吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.69,0:05:01.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.69,0:05:03.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}真是的 小心點嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.91,0:05:07.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}飽啦飽啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.20,0:05:11.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}里志那傢伙已經跑去泡溫泉了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.67,0:05:23.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}難得來一次溫泉旅館呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.88,0:05:29.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}話說折木打算去哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.80,0:05:30.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}跟你一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.31,0:05:32.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}伊原呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.35,0:05:34.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}被小孩子拉去玩了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.64,0:05:39.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}問得很突然 折木的姐姐是怎樣的人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.11,0:05:41.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}還真是突然
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.28,0:05:44.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}話說千反田是獨生子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.74,0:05:46.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}老姐啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.45,0:05:49.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}各種意義上來講是個另類
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.12,0:05:50.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}各種意義上來講又很優秀
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.99,0:05:53.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}總覺得我在什麼方面都贏不了那傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.95,0:05:58.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}本來我就沒想著要贏
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.42,0:06:03.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那麼 為什麼突然問老姐的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.38,0:06:04.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}是因為看到了善名姐妹的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.26,0:06:07.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}其實呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.84,0:06:09.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我想有兄弟姐妹
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.84,0:06:10.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}像是姐姐啊或者是弟弟
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.47,0:06:13.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}有一個讓人放不下心的對像一直在身邊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.14,0:06:15.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}你不覺得這很美妙嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.64,0:06:16.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不覺得
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.69,0:06:20.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}看來大小姐都有過於好人的傾向啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.90,0:06:22.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}太天真了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.73,0:06:25.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}兄弟姐妹什麼的實際上一點都不好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.53,0:06:30.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}這裡 似乎不是混浴呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.28,0:06:33.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那是當然啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.50,0:06:39.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}里志嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.80,0:06:48.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}爸爸 爺爺 快點
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.93,0:06:51.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.68,0:06:54.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}喔
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.93,0:06:56.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}意外地很寬敞啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.07,0:07:12.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.08,0:07:17.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}呀 奉太郎 來啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.79,0:07:20.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}這溫泉真是夠棒的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.00,0:07:21.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}感覺都滲透進身體了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.71,0:07:24.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}血液裡摻水的話很危險的唉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.29,0:07:26.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}這話還真是夠無趣的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.17,0:07:30.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不過也算是放鬆下來的證據 我就不計較了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.97,0:07:38.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}千反田嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.54,0:08:05.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}折木
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.58,0:08:07.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}怎麼了 沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.63,0:08:08.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}泡暈了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.63,0:08:09.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}誒
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.46,0:08:12.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}沒有比他更丟臉的了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.80,0:08:14.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}連我入浴時間一半都沒到
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.05,0:08:16.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}等我注意到的時候 眼睛已經在開始打轉了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.85,0:08:19.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}你這個傢伙還真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.90,0:08:29.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}真是對不起你們兩位了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.65,0:08:32.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不客氣
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.45,0:08:36.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}折木 你還真是有著不能享受活動的宿命啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.87,0:08:39.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}說得對啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.66,0:08:42.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}估計暈車那勁頭還沒過去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.79,0:08:44.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}好想吐
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.09,0:08:58.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}是千反田嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.31,0:09:01.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}折木同學 你沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.64,0:09:02.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}稍微有點
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.02,0:09:06.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}還是很燙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.98,0:09:08.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我去幫你弄一條涼毛巾吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.57,0:09:11.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不 不用了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.94,0:09:13.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我要睡了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.36,0:09:17.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}給難得的合宿活動潑了冷水 真過意不去
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.20,0:09:19.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}沒那回事的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.83,0:09:22.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}大家打算接下來講鬼故事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.00,0:09:27.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}如果待會兒身體好一些了 折木同學也請過來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.33,0:09:29.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那麼 多保重
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.13,0:09:30.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.81,0:09:42.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}還不到八點嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.39,0:09:47.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}太鼓？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.19,0:09:51.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}其實 並不是說客人多到必須要建別館的地步
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.94,0:09:55.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}隔壁房間窗子也開著啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.95,0:09:57.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}其實是有個秘密的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.41,0:09:59.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}秘密？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.66,0:10:02.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}從前 有個陰沉的客人前來住宿
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.12,0:10:05.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}於是將他安排在本館的七號房
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.04,0:10:11.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}他既不需要餐飯 也不用鋪被子 總之不許接近
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.21,0:10:13.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}但是 定金都是是照常付的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.67,0:10:14.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那時旅館也正值繁忙的時期
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.01,0:10:16.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}遇見不用服務的客人反而正好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.05,0:10:20.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}但在那晚 傳來了非常尖銳的慘叫
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.34,0:10:20.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}慘叫？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.01,0:10:27.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}在七號房裡發現一個上吊了的人影就那樣緩緩搖晃著
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.35,0:10:32.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}聽說那位客人 是因為擅用公款後逃到這裡的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.65,0:10:33.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我就等著這樣的展開呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.48,0:10:34.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}別這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.86,0:10:36.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}自從發生了這件事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.44,0:10:38.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}住在七號房的客人就紛紛說
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.03,0:10:43.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}這房間裡有什麼東西 每當夜晚就會出現影子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.41,0:10:47.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}然後第九位住在這房間的客人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.79,0:10:48.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}他發生了什麼嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.50,0:10:52.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}在晚上 因突發疾病而死掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.96,0:10:53.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}怎麼會…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.84,0:10:54.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}就得這樣發展啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.92,0:10:56.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}都說你夠了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.59,0:10:58.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}所以奶奶找人來祛魔
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.01,0:11:00.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}還建了這棟別館
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.64,0:11:03.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}都是為了防止不好的傳聞繼續傳開
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.93,0:11:06.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那間七號房是？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.43,0:11:09.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}你看 就是窗戶正對面的那間房
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.98,0:11:15.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我們住在一樓 而二樓就不怎麼去了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.40,0:11:17.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}騙人的吧 開玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.86,0:11:20.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}聽好 這件事一定要保密哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.78,0:11:22.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}實在是夠古典的鬼故事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.96,0:11:33.96,shisseki,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(1250,50)\blur1}立秋 ，七月節。立字解見春。秋，摯也，\N\N物於此而揫斂也。恰逢孟秋時節，\N\N蓋始於公曆八月七至九日間。
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.09,0:11:44.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}早上了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.93,0:11:49.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}啊 早安
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.23,0:11:49.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}早安
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.02,0:11:50.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}千反田她們呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.94,0:11:53.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}出現了…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.65,0:11:55.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}出現了啥
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.48,0:11:59.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}昨晚被一陣暖風吹醒
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.44,0:12:01.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}無意中翻了個身
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.32,0:12:06.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}就看見正對面的房間模糊地飄著一個上吊的影子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.74,0:12:08.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}驚慌失措的伊原可真是珍品啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.62,0:12:11.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}竟然錯過了這一幕 里志那傢伙真是有夠背
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.71,0:12:13.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}多謝款待
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.00,0:12:15.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}露天溫泉怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.54,0:12:17.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}非常舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.34,0:12:18.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.26,0:12:21.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}啊 還有被子也軟綿綿的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.72,0:12:23.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}是的 睡得很香
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.26,0:12:25.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}好像沒有嘉代的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.30,0:12:30.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我還真不知道摩耶姐姐害怕那種故事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.31,0:12:33.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}傳說的幽靈的話我自然是不怕啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.94,0:12:35.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}但要是正面目擊到那種東西…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.77,0:12:37.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}毛骨悚然也要有個限度啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.82,0:12:40.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}摩耶姐姐 看到了？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.78,0:12:42.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}看到了絕對看到了真的看到了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.28,0:12:44.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}姐姐 你把那件事說出來了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.53,0:12:46.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}爸爸不是告誡過不能說嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.95,0:12:49.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}吵死啦 有什麼不好嘛 反正是摩耶姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.62,0:12:55.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.88,0:13:00.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那個…  摩耶花同學所說的 你怎麼想
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.26,0:13:02.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}上吊的影子嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.01,0:13:06.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}像這種保留節目呀約定俗成的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.84,0:13:08.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}就是因為必不可少才會存留下來的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.26,0:13:12.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那麼折木同學 你覺得摩耶花同學所說的是事實嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.14,0:13:13.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不覺得
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.14,0:13:17.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那麼果然是搞錯了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.23,0:13:19.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.32,0:13:24.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我也看到了 上吊的影子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.11,0:13:29.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}摩耶花同學起床了 所以我也醒了過來
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.53,0:13:31.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}然後在黑暗中隱隱看見了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.58,0:13:34.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我也以為是搞錯了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.87,0:13:37.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}但摩耶花同學也看到了同樣的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.71,0:13:39.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}把什麼東西錯以為是上吊的人了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.92,0:13:40.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}就是昨天說的那個
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.00,0:13:42.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}鬼怪露真形…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.92,0:13:44.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}原是枯芒草嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.34,0:13:45.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.68,0:13:49.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}若是那樣的話 究竟是把什麼看錯了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.14,0:13:50.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.81,0:13:54.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那就說說究竟是把什麼看錯了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.39,0:13:55.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}為什麼我要…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.23,0:13:57.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}折木同學 一起調查吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.56,0:13:59.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我很好奇
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.61,0:14:02.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}抱歉 小千
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.94,0:14:05.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我已經說好要幫梨繪看暑假作業的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.99,0:14:09.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}包在我身上 我們一定會查清真相的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.82,0:14:10.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}對吧 折木同學
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.33,0:14:12.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}就算你說「對吧」…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.99,0:14:16.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}總而言之 必須要做的就盡快做
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.45,0:14:14.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\an8}打擾了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.50,0:14:21.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那麼 那個影子是在你房間的正對面嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.75,0:14:23.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}是的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.25,0:14:23.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}大小呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.17,0:14:26.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}似乎不大不小
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.13,0:14:27.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}形狀呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.01,0:14:29.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不太記得了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.84,0:14:30.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}顏色呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.55,0:14:32.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不清楚 因為是影子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.55,0:14:33.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}影子嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.76,0:14:36.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}就是說由於逆光所以把人看成了影子嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.52,0:14:38.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我想是的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.02,0:14:40.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}逆光啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.60,0:14:43.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}要說夜晚的光源 也就是月亮了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.77,0:14:47.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我也是這麼想的 昨晚的月亮我記得是相當明亮的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.49,0:14:49.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}這又怎麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.45,0:14:53.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}千反田 講完鬼故事睡下時是幾點
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.49,0:14:54.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那個…  十點
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.04,0:14:56.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那時的雨窗如何
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.25,0:14:57.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我想是關上的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.37,0:15:01.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}只要雨窗是關上的 就不可能有影子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.88,0:15:04.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}事情變得麻煩了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.50,0:15:08.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}既然這樣 去看看本館七號房比較好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.47,0:15:10.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}真美妙呢 撲朔迷離
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.76,0:15:12.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}果然辦了合宿真好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.85,0:15:14.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}沒辦的話才好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.39,0:15:15.39,Comment,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}禁止進入
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.48,0:15:18.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}喂
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.35,0:15:21.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}有什麼事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.90,0:15:22.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}交給你了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.15,0:15:24.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我不擅長應付小孩
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.65,0:15:24.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}好的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.57,0:15:27.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}嘉代 能來一下嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.40,0:15:32.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我們想去本館
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.28,0:15:35.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}去本館… 為什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.91,0:15:38.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我們在調查那個上吊的影子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.20,0:15:41.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}想去看看七號房
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.58,0:15:44.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}對不起 現在不行
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.96,0:15:46.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}會被姐姐罵的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.42,0:15:49.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那麼回答我一件事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.38,0:15:52.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那間房現在仍然是客房嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.68,0:15:58.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不是 現在本館只有澡堂和食堂是給客人用的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.02,0:16:00.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那麼是空房啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.60,0:16:02.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}二樓全都當作儲藏室了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.73,0:16:05.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}可以了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.19,0:16:08.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}謝謝 幫大忙…了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.40,0:16:10.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}被她討厭了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.15,0:16:14.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不是挺好嗎 可能是害怕高大的男生吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.03,0:16:16.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}這才可愛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.33,0:16:20.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}進不去七號房會不好辦嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.87,0:16:22.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}與其說不好辦 不如說是變麻煩了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.04,0:16:24.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不能勘察現場了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.67,0:16:28.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}哎呀 真是懷念的東西呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.76,0:16:35.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}清晨的廣播體操
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.76,0:16:37.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}直到去年還一直參加呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.68,0:16:41.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}直到中學二年級…  真的？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.10,0:16:45.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}後面也看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.23,0:16:49.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}昨晚下雨了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.53,0:16:51.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}嗯 下了一陣
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.74,0:16:54.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}如果要能浮現出影子的話
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.66,0:16:58.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}就必須把向東和向西的雨窗都打開
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.91,0:17:00.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.37,0:17:03.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}午飯好了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.08,0:17:06.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我吃飽了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.21,0:17:14.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}有個姐妹果然好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.34,0:17:18.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}誒 千反田同學希望有個姐妹嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.43,0:17:19.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}嗯 是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.72,0:17:20.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}於是 查到什麼了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.35,0:17:21.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.97,0:17:23.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}現在還只是先行調查
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.56,0:17:24.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}雖說我已經有了個假設
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.27,0:17:26.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}說來聽聽
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.11,0:17:31.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我說 你們這是在談些什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.19,0:17:33.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}居然把我排除在外
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.36,0:17:35.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不是我們把你排除在外
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.32,0:17:37.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}倒是你先前都到哪裡鬼混去了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.78,0:17:38.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}完全不見蹤影
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.91,0:17:40.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}你還真就不懂啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.66,0:17:43.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}溫泉就得反復地泡才是正確做法啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.16,0:17:44.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}還有這麼一回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.54,0:17:47.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}怎麼樣哇 人家的浴衣～
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.83,0:17:48.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}好漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.88,0:17:49.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不賴嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.59,0:17:53.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}一放暑假的時候終於買給我了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.42,0:17:54.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\blur5}你一直很想要嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.97,0:17:56.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}品味還算不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.30,0:17:59.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\blur5}兔子圖案的也非常可愛呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.47,0:17:57.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}什麼不好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.39,0:18:03.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\blur5}挺成熟的 覺得也不錯哇
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.01,0:18:00.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那條腰帶 是假結啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.22,0:18:02.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}什麼東西突然嫁接了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.72,0:18:04.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\blur5}腰帶好可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.85,0:18:05.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不是嫁接 是假結啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.85,0:18:05.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\blur5}很合身 很合身
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.93,0:18:08.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}只有腰帶的結是特別裝上去的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.10,0:18:10.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我可不承認這是浴衣
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.19,0:18:12.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}你還真是無聊啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.07,0:18:17.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.41,0:18:23.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}看來我也中了上吊的詛咒了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.25,0:18:31.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}去昨天的溫泉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.54,0:18:32.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.13,0:18:35.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}上吊的影子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.21,0:18:41.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那只是伊原和千反田的幻覺 也就是乾枯的芒草
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.22,0:18:44.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不過還不差臨門一腳
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.31,0:18:50.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}洗完一起出來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.69,0:18:53.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}或許是里志吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.49,0:18:59.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}你剛才不是還在餐廳嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.95,0:19:01.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}你是什麼時候來的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.62,0:19:05.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}從青山莊後崖上滑下來正好是這裡的後面
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.50,0:19:09.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}為了抄近路居然滑下山崖
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.58,0:19:10.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}真像里志的做風
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.96,0:19:18.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}找不到可以讓千反田信服的解釋
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.88,0:19:21.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}影子的本體並不是很難解釋
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.09,0:19:24.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}難是難在為什麼要那麼做
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.52,0:19:28.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}奉太郎 你該不會是泡溫泉泡暈了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.98,0:19:31.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那個 昨晚有什麼活動嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.40,0:19:33.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}泡昏了的奉太郎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.69,0:19:34.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不是這個啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.15,0:19:37.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}啊 是大家一起講鬼故事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.73,0:19:39.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}左擁右抱還多出一個
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.57,0:19:41.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不 更加正式的大型活動
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.11,0:19:43.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}對了 有個夏日祭典
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.32,0:19:45.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不是都能聽到太鼓音嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.41,0:19:47.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}太鼓…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.50,0:19:50.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}對啊 夏日祭典啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.67,0:19:52.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.17,0:19:54.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}嗯？那個怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.43,0:20:04.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}上吊的影子 那個啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.72,0:20:08.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}是掛在衣架上的浴衣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.89,0:20:13.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}為什麼那個地方會有浴衣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.31,0:20:18.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}而且 還特地把雨窗打開讓我們看到浴衣影子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.44,0:20:18.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}這太奇怪了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.11,0:20:20.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不是為了給你們看的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.49,0:20:21.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.53,0:20:23.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}是為了晾乾…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.41,0:20:25.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}濕掉的浴衣
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.37,0:20:30.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}打開滑窗只是為了保證通風讓浴衣乾的快一點
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.95,0:20:31.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.46,0:20:33.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}因為下雨了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.83,0:20:34.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我問的不是這個
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.67,0:20:36.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}為什麼偏偏是7號房間呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.59,0:20:40.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}為了不讓人看到正在晾這的浴衣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.42,0:20:41.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}可是我們看到了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.92,0:20:44.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不是 是為了不讓她的家人看到
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.55,0:20:46.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.39,0:20:50.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}晾浴衣的是嘉代
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.22,0:20:53.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}嘉代羨慕梨繪的浴衣
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.39,0:20:54.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}於是就想試穿一下
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.10,0:20:56.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不過梨繪應該不肯借給她的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.15,0:20:59.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}為什麼啊 她們可是姐妹啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.32,0:21:00.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}你還沒有發覺嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.11,0:21:04.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}梨繪她啊 無論是茶杯 廣播操簽到卡還是球
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.61,0:21:07.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}只要是自己的東西就會分的很清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.16,0:21:11.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}嘉代沒辦法向這樣的梨繪提出借浴衣的請求
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.87,0:21:12.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}怎麼會這樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.75,0:21:15.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}可是嘉代又十分想去參加
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.83,0:21:19.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}所以把浴衣拿走 穿著它去參加了昨天的夏日祭典
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.09,0:21:21.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}時間是8點
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.21,0:21:23.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}嘉代去參加夏日祭典了？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.97,0:21:24.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我看到了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.30,0:21:27.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}昨天晚上8點的時候看到了一個從家裡出去的身影
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.47,0:21:33.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}嘉代看來昨天講鬼故事的時候不在場呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.48,0:21:35.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}嘉代確實沒來
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.35,0:21:39.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}就在這時 正開心的參加祭典的嘉代卻遇到了不幸的事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.44,0:21:41.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}開始下雨了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.98,0:21:45.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}雖然雨很快的停了 但是浴衣卻弄濕了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.24,0:21:48.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}嘉代想起了明天預定去放煙火的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.37,0:21:52.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}梨繪毫無疑問會穿這件浴衣然後去放煙火的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.41,0:21:56.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不管怎樣一定要在明天之前把浴衣晾乾 不然會被梨繪責怪
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.04,0:22:01.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}晾在本館的一層會被家人發現 別館則不再考慮範圍
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.80,0:22:03.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}大晚上的又不能用烘乾機
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.96,0:22:07.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}所以嘉代看準了大家都睡著了安靜下來的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.55,0:22:10.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}就在本館2層最裡面的房間裡晾乾浴衣
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.39,0:22:13.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}這之後嘉代的不幸還在繼續
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.14,0:22:16.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}從打開的窗戶裡月光照了進來
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.89,0:22:18.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}讓人看上去就像是上吊了的影子
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.02,0:22:24.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}最後的不幸就是 我們開始調查上吊的影子
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.32,0:22:27.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}對於嘉代來說這就如坐針氈
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.82,0:22:31.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}估計那時候在和室臥室裡一閃而過的影子絕對是嘉代沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.54,0:22:34.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嘉代…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.37,0:22:37.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}浴衣在第二天一早就放回了原處
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.12,0:22:41.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不同於梨繪 嘉代是每天都去參加廣播體操
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.71,0:22:43.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}要趁早放回原處也不是那麼困難的事
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.38,0:22:46.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}是這樣子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.97,0:22:48.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}這件事請對伊原保密
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.72,0:22:51.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}因為對誰來說都有各種各樣所謂的私人問題啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.35,0:22:55.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}如此一來
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.39,0:23:00.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}她們兩人的關係就變得看上去並不好
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.36,0:23:05.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}是個連浴衣都不能隨便借來借去的姐妹
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.62,0:23:16.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}所謂的兄弟姐妹 不就是那回事嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.16,0:23:18.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我一直希望有兄弟姐妹
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.66,0:23:22.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}值得尊敬的姐姐或者是惹人憐愛的弟弟
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.01,0:23:30.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}千反田所希望的那種兄弟姐妹
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.72,0:23:33.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}或許僅僅是乾枯的芒草而已啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.89,0:23:38.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}好熱 嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.31,0:23:42.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}能行吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.15,0:23:43.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.66,0:24:00.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}看來 或許也不是只有枯芒草啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:25:37.59,0:25:40.93,chapter,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,0)\bord0\blur10\t(0,300,\blur2)\t(250,300,\bord2)\pos(630,320)}去參加試映會吧!\N
